title: Ep288 Navajo Nation Crimes
description:
This week, the gals head back to the Reservation to take a look at just a few f*cked up local cases. Topics include an exhaustive desert search, a regrettable pickup, and a very, very, very long walk. Stock up on wines from Nk'Mip Cellars, learn your history, and tune in for Navajo Nation Crimes.
